column5: this is my first ice fishing for lake trout.. Ive done most of the time ice fishing for perch.. but wondering, where do i need to go in simcoe.. to fish for this type of fish..  thnx bfisher
Follow the crowds.  You already know the place to walk out from (IBP)
You don't have to go far to get into Deep water off IBP.. drill a hole and fish... nothing .. move. Whitie's roam.. it's all about finding their "runway" and being there when they come thru.
